ActConstitution Act, 1867
SubjectAdministrator of the Government of Manitoba
PrecisAppointment to serve as ADMINISTRATOR of the Government of MANITOBA (1) the Hon. MICHEL MONNIN from September 18 to 21, 2012, and from September 25 to 26, 2012, inclusive; and (2) the Hon. GLENN D. JOYAL from October 2 to 5, 2012, and from October 16 to 17, 2012, inclusive; and (3) the Hon. MARC M. MONNIN from October 22 to 26, 2012, inclusive.
